---
title: Tex-Mex Pork Rissoles & Paprika Cheesy Fries with Charred Corn Salsa & Sour Cream
description: Rissoles, that classic family staple, gets a dash of Tex-Mex spice mixed into the pork mixture to really stir the pot. With smoked paprika cheesy fries and a fresh salsa, this meal shines a whole new light on a tried-and-true dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mexican-pork-rissoles-paprika-cheesy-fries-4a093f59.jpg
